## Input

```css
@supports #{"(display: grid)"} {
  a {
    display: grid;
  }
}

@supports #{"(display: grid)"} and (gap: 1rem) {
  a {
    gap: 1rem;
  }
}

@supports not #{"(display: flex)"} {
  a {
    display: block;
  }
}

@supports (gap: 1rem) and #{"(display: grid)"} {
  a {
    gap: 1rem;
  }
}

@supports (gap: 1rem) or #{"(display: flex)"} {
  a {
    display: flex;
  }
}

```


